    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >亮剑吧！猫猫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立属于自己的营地，并击败所有敢于冒犯的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻量化的策略游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053290/extras/a9b746b21932a38d1213646239b1776b.avif?t=1766080881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053290/extras_big/a9b746b21932a38d1213646239b1776b.avif?t=1766080881 width=800 height=450 /></span>相比于经典的策略游戏，《喵喵与共》更偏向于轻量化：没有复杂的经济系统，不需要极高的切屏速度，不需要精细的操作，不需要排兵布阵。你需要做的只是带领你的小猫们击败敌人，并用获得的宝石召集更多的小猫，或是建造箭塔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >搭配你的兵种、英雄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053290/extras/ff69089c853930405fc81a13e3c41ab0.avif?t=1766080881\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053290/extras_big/ff69089c853930405fc81a13e3c41ab0.avif?t=1766080881 width=800 height=450 /></span>不同定位的兵种在数值上存在显著的差异，更好的搭配不同的兵种将会帮助你更好的应对来袭的敌人。同时也要注意，敌我双方的英雄角色和他们的技能也将左右游戏的胜负。</p>",
